Class SpotlightImageProperty

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cube.storm.ui.model.Model

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class SpotlightImageProperty
extends AnimationFrame
    Image property for SpotlightListItem. Contains text to be overlaid on the image, a link to push to when a specific frame is clicked, a delay, and the image to display.
